</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-04-02-0118-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-03-04-02-0118-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-04-02-0119" class="document">Sullivan, Greene, and Stirling to GW, this date</a>. See also <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-04-02-0104" class="document">GW to Samuel Tucker, 24 April 1776</a>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-04-02-0118-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-03-04-02-0118-fn-0002">2</a>

   <p>GW inadvertently wrote in informed in the manuscript.</p>

